                <Property key="Caption" value="This is a dashboard layout/texture used for the interior dashboard on older vehicles.\nYou can specify a different dashboard mod to be used, by editing `ui_default_truck_dash` in \config\RoR.cfg\nNormal on-screen dashboard mods will not work. It has to be a specific layout, like this one."/>
